{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.1","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:1","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.002.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Pr\u00e9dication de Jonas \u00e0 Ninive. Repentance des Ninivites<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. (Lu 11:29, 30, 32. J\u00e9 18:7, 8.) 1 R 21:27-29. Jo\u00eb 2:12-20. \u00c9s 55:7-11.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel fut adress\u00e9e \u00e0 Jonas une seconde fois, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2","name":"Jonas 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.2.11","name":"Jonas 2:11","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.2.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:2","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>L\u00e8ve-toi, va \u00e0 Ninive, la grande ville, et proclames-y la publication que je t\u2019ordonne!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3","name":"Jonas 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.1","name":"Jonas 3:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:3","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Et Jonas se leva, et alla \u00e0 Ninive, selon la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel. Or Ninive \u00e9tait une tr\u00e8s grande ville, de trois jours de marche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4","name":"Jonas 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2","name":"Jonas 3:2","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:4","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Jonas fit d\u2019abord dans la ville une journ\u00e9e de marche; il criait et disait: Encore quarante jours, et Ninive est d\u00e9truite!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5","name":"Jonas 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3","name":"Jonas 3:3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:5","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Les gens de Ninive crurent \u00e0 Dieu, ils publi\u00e8rent un je\u00fbne, et se rev\u00eatirent de sacs, depuis les plus grands jusqu\u2019aux plus petits.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6","name":"Jonas 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4","name":"Jonas 3:4","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:6","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>La chose parvint au roi de Ninive; il se leva de son tr\u00f4ne, \u00f4ta son manteau, se couvrit d\u2019un sac, et s\u2019assit sur la cendre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7","name":"Jonas 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5","name":"Jonas 3:5","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:7","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Et il fit faire dans Ninive cette publication, par ordre du roi et de ses grands; Que les hommes et les b\u00eates, les b\u0153ufs et les brebis, ne go\u00fbtent de rien, ne paissent point, et ne boivent point d\u2019eau!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8","name":"Jonas 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6","name":"Jonas 3:6","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:8","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Que les hommes et les b\u00eates soient couverts de sacs, qu\u2019ils crient \u00e0 Dieu avec force, et qu\u2019ils reviennent tous de leur mauvaise voie et des actes de violence dont leurs mains sont coupables!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9","name":"Jonas 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7","name":"Jonas 3:7","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:9","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.003.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>Qui sait si Dieu ne reviendra pas et ne se repentira pas, et s\u2019il ne renoncera pas \u00e0 son ardente col\u00e8re, en sorte que nous ne p\u00e9rissions point?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.10","name":"Jonas 3:10","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8","name":"Jonas 3:8","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.10","label":"","reference":"Jonas 3:10","prev_osis_id":"Jonah.003.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Jonah.004.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Jonah.3.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Dieu vit qu\u2019ils agissaient ainsi et qu\u2019ils revenaient de leur mauvaise voie. Alors Dieu se repentit du mal qu\u2019il avait r\u00e9solu de leur faire, et il ne le fit pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3","name":"Jonas 3","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.4.1","name":"Jonas 4:1","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.4.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9","name":"Jonas 3:9","id":"fra-LSG:Jonah.3.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbd788341.31223499');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd788341.31223499\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbd788341.31223499","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbd788341.31223499'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd788341.31223499\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}